(64, 1, '2019-06-19 08:49:07', '2019-06-19 08:49:07', 'VIETNAM ELEVATOR EXPO 2020 - Networking and Sharing for Mutual Success\r\n\r\nAs ‘a commercial playground’ in the right spirit of global economic flow focusing on ‘Networking and Sharing’, the exhibition is the place where new technologies are launched, resilient activities like business-matching, investment attraction or consultancy are initiated; and advanced seminars on commercial policies or development strategies are held.\r\n\r\nThe elevator pitch for the industry - Vietnam Elevator Expo 2020 would identify the potential of the industry by mapping the interest, capabilities and expertise that Vietnam elevators and escalators has to offer.  It is creating the right channels by generating high-quality leads and providing business opportunities.\r\n\r\nIt is a must-attend for: OEMS, Elevator and Escalator Component Suppliers, Builders and Developers, Architects, Civil &amp; Electrical Engineers, Project Management Consultants, Service Consultants, Engineering &amp; Architect Students, Corporates, Independent Enthusiastic, Government Contracts, Facility Managers, Distributors, Hospital Administrators, Business Entrepreneurs.', 'About Elevator 2020', 'With the history of being one of the most prestigious and long-standing trade promotion events in Vietnam, Vietnam Expo has always affirmed that through every year of organization and in 2019 - after a year of prosperity of the Vietnamese economy. Men, import-export turnover and investment all have signs of encouraging growth, we continue to promote the role of an event to promote import-export trade and investment, bringing Vietnamese products to promote. to the world and vice versa.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about-elevator-2020', '', '', '2019-07-05 21:01:17', '2019-07-05 14:01:17', '', 0, 'http://elevator_vnexpo.co/?p=64', 0, 'post', '', 0);
