(189, 1, '2019-06-22 21:50:29', '2019-06-22 14:50:29', '<div id="pl-189"  class="panel-layout" ><div id="pg-189-0"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style"  data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}"  data-ratio="1"  data-ratio-direction="right" ><div id="pgc-189-0-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="1" ><div id="panel-189-0-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="0" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div class="textwidget">A hugely popular feature of the event is always the free seminar sessions. In 2020, the stellar line up of speakers will deliver thought-provoking and professionally focussed series of talks and presentations on topics such as connectivity, evacuation, modernisation and safety, as well as the latest on new standards and regulations.\n\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-460 aligncenter" src="http://elevatorexpo.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/presentation2-600x400.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="400" />\n\nSessions start at 9.30 each day - so make sure that you are there early to get a seat. They are operated on a first come, first served basis.</div></div></div></div></div>', 'Seminar programme', 'An extremely popular feature of this event is always free seminars. In 2019, outstanding speakers will present a series of professional talks and presentations on thinking and focus on topics such as connectivity, evacuation, modernization and safety, as well as the latest. about new standards and regulations.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'seminar-programme', '', '', '2019-07-03 22:29:05', '2019-07-03 15:29:05', '', 0, 'http://elevator_vnexpo.co/?p=189', 0, 'post', '', 0),
