(207, 1, '2019-06-22 22:06:16', '2019-06-22 15:06:16', '“Success is just the first step for the next attempt”\r\n\r\nAs a result of enormous effort of the Organizer and active participation of exhibitors, VIETNAM HARDWARE &amp; HAND TOOLS 2019 has achieved surprisingly impressive results. More than 283 enterprises from 18 different countries and territories exhibited on the scale of 5000m2, Belgium, China, Denmark, Germany, Hong Kong, Italy, India, Japan, Korea, Malaysia, Russia, Singapore, Spain, Switzerland, Thailand, Taiwan, USA, Vietnam. In addition, there are a wide range of the world major brands joining the Exhibition such as: BOSCH, ONISHI, KNIPEX, WIHA, WEDO, UNIQUE STAR, SWISSTECH, PUMA, KUNJEK, ITO, SB CORPORATION, NANIWA, STAR-M, THE HIVE, OMBRA, KENDO TOOLS, etc., along with Vietnamese brands like LIDOVIT, ANH DUONG, NHAT THANG, DINH LUC, T.A.T, TAN AN PHAT, MINH KHANG, SDS, MRO, etc., were on display. This is a significant event supporting the key industries to develop sustainably, namely: construction, automobile, road, shipbuilding, aerospace, woodworking, retail etc.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe organizer organized several commercial connection activities between sellers and buyers, including forum about Hardware and Hand Tools industry, Seminar: “ Enhancing Living Standards and Home Improvements: Trends and Best Practices in The Global Manufacturing Chain”, Seminar: “Responsibility Requirements and Social Standards According to the Electronic Industry Citizenship Coalition (EICC) - An “Entrance Ticket” for Enterprises in the industries of Mechanics, Hardware, Electricity and Electronics to Enter The Global Manufacturing Chain”. Both, exhibitors and visitors were contented with their participation, and signed many contracts and business cooperation agreements. Following above success, VIETNAM HARDWARE &amp; HAND TOOLS 2020 will be held from 18th June to 20th Dec, 2020 at Hanoi International Exhibition Center (ICE) 91 Tran Hung Dao Str., Hoan Kiem Dist., Hanoi, Vietnam.The exhibition is expected to attract 300 enterprises from 20 different countries and territories exhibiting on the area of 5.000m2 and welcome 15.000 visitors during four exhibition days. This year, the exhibition continues to have its honor of being supported by Vietnam Association of Mechanical Industry (VAMI) and Ho Chi Minh City’s Association of Mechanical – Electrical Enterprises (HAMEE) with consultancy for all activities before and during the exhibition.', 'VIETNAM INTERNATIONAL HARDWARE & HANDTOOLS EXHIBITION – VIETNAM HARDWARE & HAND TOOLS 2020', 'The success of Vietnam Expo is not only a first-ever trade promotion event of Vietnam held annually for nearly three decades. It is also a well-known event because of the diversity of products, quality products - prestigious brand - creativity of Vietnam that introduces international friends.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vietnam-expo-capture-opportunities-cooperate-and-grow-together', '', '', '2019-07-04 10:32:36', '2019-07-04 03:32:36', '', 0, 'http://elevator_vnexpo.co/?p=207', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(208, 1, '2019-06-22 23:59:00', '2019-06-22 16:59:00', '<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">“Vietnam Expo - Connecting, sharing, and succeeding” is the message that Vietnam Expo International Trade Fair has built and brought.</span></span>\r\n<figure><img class="wp-image-146 size-full aligncenter" src="http://vietnamexpo.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/vietnam-expo-nam-bat-thoi-co-hop-tac-va-cung-phat-trien1548650334.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="427" /></figure>\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Deputy Minister of Industry and Trade Tran Quoc Khanh at Vietnam Expo 2018</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">The success of Vietnam Expo is not only a first-ever trade promotion event of Vietnam held annually for nearly three decades. </span><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">It is also a well-known event because of the diversity of products, quality products - prestigious brand - creativity of Vietnam that introduces to international friends.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone wp-image-205 size-full" src="http://elevatorexpo.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/5_qxvg.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="663" />\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Vietnam Expo is a key event chaired by the Ministry of Industry and Trade (Trade Promotion Agency), receiving strong support from local ministries, domestic and foreign promotion organizations, Vinexad company is responsible The deployment will take place in 4 days, from April 10-13, 2019 at the International Exhibition Center (ICE) - 91 Tran Hung Dao, Hanoi.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">In 2018, Vietnam Expo gathered 500 businesses from 23 countries and territories, including 6 international pavilions from the Federal Republic of Russia, Cuba, South Korea, Nepal, China and Vietnam. </span><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">A special feature of Vietnam Expo is the diverse and unique products that are exhibited specifically in each area including: International pavilion zone - National Brand Area (Vietnam Value) - Machinery and Equipment Product Zone - Food and drink area.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">“We have thoroughly prepared for the launch of the latest automatic assembly line at Vietnam Expo, our goal is to meet Japanese and Korean electronic component manufacturing companies during the event. This ”, Representative of Intech Vietnam Co. </span><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">share.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Ms. Nguyen Thi Oanh, General Director of Hoang Minh Joint Stock Company said: “This is the second time I joined Vietnam Expo, I assess the quality of the business here is very potential, because the requirements of customers are very high. For environmentally friendly adhesive tape products, manufactured entirely by natural rubber, no artificial additives, no toxic chemicals, good adhesion on all material surfaces, easily torn by hand. </span><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">We confidently affirm that our products meet the standards to supply for large corporations, because we compete with the quality and originality that not all products have. ”</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">In the same view, Mr. Nguyen Van Ly, Viglacera''s representative, said: “We realize that after each fair is very effective, we have a large number of customers, especially international visitors. We are interested in new products with environmental friendly elements such as V-Smart smart hygiene, White-bone Granite tiles, energy-saving glass, baked clay bricks ... Through Vietnam Expo, we want to strengthen more 