ays*</li>\n 	<li>Delivers thousands of senior decision-making visitors who are there to buy</li>\n</ul></div></div></div><div id="pgc-84-1-1"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="0.5" ><div id="panel-84-1-1-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="2" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div class="textwidget"><ul class="ul_check">\n 	<li>Organised and run by LEIA (Lift and Escalator Industry Association)</li>\n 	<li>Staged only once every three years</li>\n 	<li>Supported by over 100 UK &amp; international exhibitors</li>\n 	<li>Network with your UK and global peers</li>\n</ul></div></div></div></div></div>', 'Why exhibit', 'No other event gathers many important decision makers over a two-day period. More than 2,700 visitors with real purchasing power attended the exhibition, all looking forward to meeting new suppliers, finding new products, networks and forming new business relationships.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '84-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-23 15:36:15', '2019-06-23 08:36:15', '', 84, 'http://elevator_vnexpo.co/84-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
