(408, 1, '2019-07-03 20:11:35', '2019-07-03 13:11:35', '<div id="pl-8"  class="panel-layout" ><div id="pg-8-0"  class="panel-grid panel-has-style"  data-style="{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;introduce_index&quot;,&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}"  data-ratio="1"  data-ratio-direction="right" ><div class="introduce_index panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-8-0" ><div id="pgc-8-0-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="1" ><div id="panel-8-0-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="0" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><h3 class="widget-title">WELCOME TO VIETNAM ELEVATOR EXPO 2020</h3><div class="textwidget">VIETNAM ELEVATOR EXPO – International Lifts, Elevators Technologies &amp; Accessories Expo 2020 is going to be taken place at Hanoi International Center For Exhibition (ICE) – 91 Tran Hung Dao Hanoi City from 18 June to 20 June 2020.\n\nThe Expo has become an event in elevator industry worldwide under the support of domestic and foreign exhibitors, visitors, friends in this industry and colleagues. In the three-day exhibition, domestic and foreign exhibitors have shown their own arts and skills which contains the advancing products and technology.\n\nToday tall towers dominate the scene in the metros indicating the way forward for evolving cities and towns. The International Elevator and Escalator Expo is designed specifically to offer you a premium platform at witnessing technological innovations, aesthetic designs and the progress in the vertical transportation industry.\n\nWe hope that you would be interested in participating in the booth to promote products, find partners, meet and exchange experiences, invest in cooperation ... contribute to promoting business in the elevator industry potential in Vietnam.</div></div></div></div></div></div>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-07-03 20:11:35', '2019-07-03 13:11:35', '', 8, 'http://elevatorexpo.com.vn/8-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
