(455, 1, '2019-07-03 22:23:46', '2019-07-03 15:23:46', 'WHO CAN ATTEND VIETNAM ELEVATOR EXPO 2020?\r\n\r\nVIETNAM ELEVATOR EXPO 2020 is targeted for all those in the trade sector whose responsibility it is to manage, specify, install, modernise or maintain lifts and escalators in any kind of private, commercial or public-sector building: lift contractors, consultants, engineers, local authority representatives, facilities managers, architects, facilities managers, quantity surveyors, disability service providers, property developers and managers.\r\n\r\nWHAT TIME DO THE DOORS OPEN?\r\n\r\nThe halls open for visitors at 9:00am each day.\r\n\r\nCAN I BRING CHILDREN?\r\n\r\nChildren under 16 are not permitted to enter the show except in special circumstances and by prior arrangement with the organisers.\r\n\r\nI AM A STUDENT, AM I ABLE TO ATTEND THE EVENT?\r\n\r\nYes, students are welcome. You will need to present your student card at the registration desk you to gain entry. Head to the LEIA stand for advice and guidance on starting a career in the lift industry.', 'FAQ', 'LIFTEX 2019 is targeted for all commercial industry members who are responsible for managing, designating, installing, modernizing or maintaining elevators and escalators in any type of private, commercial or public: elevator contractors, consultants, engineers, local government representatives, facility managers, architects, facility managers, quantitative investigators, and service providers disability, developer and property manager.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '160-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-07-03 22:23:46', '2019-07-03 15:23:46', '', 160, 'http://elevatorexpo.com.vn/160-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(456, 1, '2019-07-03 22:24:04', '2019-07-03 15:24:04', 'WHO CAN ATTEND VIETNAM ELEVATOR EXPO 2020?\r\n\r\nVIETNAM ELEVATOR EXPO 2020 is targeted for all those in the trade sector whose responsibility it is to manage, specify, install, modernise or maintain lifts and escalators in any kind of private, commercial or public-sector building: lift contractors, consultants, engineers, local authority representatives, facilities managers, architects, facilities managers, quantity surveyors, disability service providers, property developers and managers.\r\n\r\nWHAT TIME DO THE DOORS OPEN?\r\n\r\nThe halls open for visitors at 9:00am each day.\r\n\r\nCAN I BRING CHILDREN?\r\n\r\nChildren under 16 are not permitted to enter the show except in special circumstances and by prior arrangement with the organisers.\r\n\r\nI AM A STUDENT, AM I ABLE TO ATTEND THE EVENT?\r\n\r\nYes, students are welcome. You will need to present your student card at the registration desk you to gain entry. Head to the LEIA stand for advice and guidance on starting a career in the lift industry.', 'FAQ', 'LIFTEX 2019 được nhắm mục tiêu cho tất cả những người trong ngành thương mại có trách nhiệm quản lý, chỉ định, cài đặt, hiện đại hóa hoặc bảo trì thang máy và thang cuốn trong bất kỳ loại công trình tư nhân, thương mại hoặc công cộng nào: nhà thầu thang máy, tư vấn, kỹ sư, chính quyền địa phương đại diện, quản lý cơ sở, kiến ​​trúc sư, quản lý cơ sở, điều tra viên số lượng, nhà cung cấp dịch vụ khuyết tật, nhà phát triển và quản lý tài sản.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '154-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-07-03 22:24:04', '2019-07-03 15:24:04', '', 154, 'http://elevatorexpo.com.vn/154-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
