dustry has limited processing capacity with parts and components importation basically. The Vietnam elevator market is growing rapidly with $74.76 million in 2017 and is expected to reach $160 million by 2025. The Vietnamese government plans to build 13 subway lines in Ho Chi Minh and Hanoi by 2025. New subways and other infrastructure will bring a lot of opportunities for elevator companies.\n\n&nbsp;</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="pg-w5d1f5d7c9ef43-3"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style"  data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}"  data-ratio="1"  data-ratio-direction="right" ><div id="pgc-w5d1f5d7c9ef43-3-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="1" ><div id="panel-w5d1f5d7c9ef43-3-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_siteorigin-panels-builder panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="3" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div id="pl-w5d1f5d7c9ef8d"  class="panel-layout" ><div id="pg-w5d1f5d7c9ef8d-0"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style"  data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}"  data-ratio="1"  data-ratio-direction="right" ><div id="pgc-w5d1f5d7c9ef8d-0-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="1" ><div id="panel-w5d1f5d7c9ef8d-0-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="0" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><h3 class="widget-title">Rental Options</h3><div class="textwidget"></div></div></div></div><div id="pg-w5d1f5d7c9ef8d-1"  class="panel-grid panel-no-style"  data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;}"  data-ratio="1"  data-ratio-direction="right" ><div id="pgc-w5d1f5d7c9ef8d-1-0"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="0.5" ><div id="panel-w5d1f5d7c9ef8d-1-0-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="1" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div class="textwidget"><img src="http://elevatorexpo.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/rental-600x400.png" alt="" width="600" height="400" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-126" /></div></div></div><div id="pgc-w5d1f5d7c9ef8d-1-1"  class="panel-grid-cell"  data-weight="0.5" ><div id="panel-w5d1f5d7c9ef8d-1-1-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="2" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div class="textwidget">1. Package stand: 9 sqm\n• Carpeted (3m x 3m)\n• 03 partitions\n• Fascia with company name\n• 01 in formation counter\n• 02 chairs\n• 01 waste paper basket\n• 02 fluorescent tubes\n• 01 electric socket of 05 Amp/220V\n2. Space only\n• Indoor raw space: minimum are\n18 sq.m Exhibitors will build their own\nstands Electricity and carpet are not\navailable</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>', 'Product Zone', 'Vietnam Expo 2019 will take place from April 10-13, 2019 at the 91 Tran Hung Dao Exhibition Center, Hoan Kiem, Hanoi, displaying and introducing many new technology products.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '130-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-07-05 21:23:56', '2019-07-05 14:23:56', '', 130, 'http://elevatorexpo.com.vn/130-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
